reviewText: Thank you for this video. I first saw this story on the Discovery Channel and it touched my heart. Ever since, I've wanted a video of this wonderful documentary. I am enjoying it now! A Little Duck Tale - A Charming True-life Tale of Growing Up.
Ordered the movie for some older friends. Sorry I'm late I'm late in reviewing. Wanted to give them a chance to watch it. Thanks for the fast service and they loved the movie.
